13:35.072 --> 13:36.572
What do you want?

13:36.672 --> 13:38.639
It's okay.

13:38.739 --> 13:41.172
We just need proof of life.

13:41.272 --> 13:44.407
No. No. No. No!

13:44.407 --> 13:46.639
No-- Ahh! Ahh!

