I thought it would be prudent

13:56.206 --> 13:58.839
to do a point-by-point review
of all the information

13:58.939 --> 14:00.706
that we've gathered to date.

14:00.806 --> 14:02.106
So, to start, I...

14:02.206 --> 14:04.206
Sorry, I have Chloe for you.

14:04.306 --> 14:05.739
Uh, hard pass.

14:05.839 --> 14:07.906
She says it's important.

14:12.539 --> 14:15.072
Un-fucking-believable.

14:19.139 --> 14:20.072
What's up, honey?

14:20.172 --> 14:21.407
<i>Hey, Mom.</i>

14:21.407 --> 14:22.872
Everything okay?
<i>No.</i>

14:22.972 --> 14:24.272
<i>Mommy went to the store
and I forgot to tell her</i>

14:24.407 --> 14:26.139
<i>I wanted Pringles.</i>

14:26.239 --> 14:27.440
Seriously?

14:27.539 --> 14:29.772
Well, why are you calling me
and not her?

14:29.872 --> 14:31.172
<i>I did, but she won't answer.</i>

14:31.272 --> 14:33.539
Well, she just left
her phone in the car.

14:33.639 --> 14:35.139
Like she always does.

14:35.239 --> 14:37.672
Guess you're just gonna have
to rough it today, Chloe.

14:37.772 --> 14:39.239
<i>But Mom...</i>

14:39.407 --> 14:41.872
Sorry, there's Mac Cheezies
on top of the fridge.

14:41.972 --> 14:44.739
And no more calls,
unless it's an emergency.

14:44.839 --> 14:47.072
Um, otherwise, text.

14:57.539 --> 14:59.972
What the hell?

15:02.172 --> 15:04.039
Hailey, you're with Ed,
you know what to do.

15:04.139 --> 15:06.472
- I'll see you at 4:00.
- Okay.

15:06.572 --> 15:08.072
As for you,

15:08.172 --> 15:10.272
I have a pickup in Yonkers.
It's important.

15:12.872 --> 15:15.407
The ex-wife you neglected
to tell me about.

15:18.839 --> 15:20.039
How'd you know about that?

15:20.139 --> 15:22.239
Oh, you lied to me.

15:22.407 --> 15:25.172
Well, not technically,
you never asked.

15:25.272 --> 15:27.306
Her name is Liv,
she's expecting you,

15:27.407 --> 15:29.572
and I know I can count
on you to keep her safe.

15:29.672 --> 15:30.906
Mm-hmm.

15:33.239 --> 15:34.472
Hey.

15:34.572 --> 15:37.406
Please try not to scare her unnecessarily.

15:38.439 --> 15:40.272
All right.

16:16.106 --> 16:18.139
Everything's a lie.

16:19.506 --> 16:22.806
Like... my marriage.

16:22.906 --> 16:25.406
