16:52.239 --> 16:53.972
I'm pretty sure he would've...

16:54.072 --> 16:55.972
he would've killed
if you didn't, Ed.

16:56.072 --> 16:57.739
Do you think he had a family?

16:57.839 --> 16:58.739
HAILEY [chuckling]:
What?

16:58.839 --> 17:01.306
I... I don't know.

17:01.406 --> 17:03.039
He at least had a dog,
don't you think?

17:03.139 --> 17:05.106
I-I have no idea. Listen--

17:05.206 --> 17:06.906
What if his dog has one of those

17:07.006 --> 17:08.772
hard-to-adopt personalities?

17:08.872 --> 17:11.206
You know, protective...
and nippy.

17:11.306 --> 17:12.706
Do you think they
put him down yet?

17:12.806 --> 17:14.439
